Name: LoopInvGen
Version: 0.6b
Synopsis: A tool for synthesizing loop invariants.
Authors: Saswat Padhi <padhi@cs.ucla.edu>
License: LGPL with OCaml linking exception

Description: LoopInvGen uses the PIE technique for learning sufficient loop
             invariants for benchmarks in SyGuS-INV format.
Homepage: https://github.com/SaswatPadhi/LoopInvGen

OASISFormat: 0.4
BuildTools: ocamlbuild
Plugins: META (0.4), DevFiles (0.4)




